  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Abyss Chaser is an action rogue-like dungeon crawler that combines melee and ranged combat with supernatural themes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a path of vengeance as Abaddon - wrongfully disgraced rebel angel who travels the forsaken wasteland on his motorcycle hunting demons.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/3270ee2d6dbc6a5add622a2d75b90ee7.poster.avif?t=1763136040\" width=800 height=482 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/3270ee2d6dbc6a5add622a2d75b90ee7.webm?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/3270ee2d6dbc6a5add622a2d75b90ee7.mp4?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow in power during your Hunts, build your arsenal of weapons, gain support of otherworldly patrons and reclaim what's rightfully yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Abyss Chaser you complete Hunts in procedurally generated levels searching for one of demons that corrupt this land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For every run you can choose your equipment: Blade, Gun and a magical Amulet. You also get random spells and abilities from patrons that support you during the Hunt.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/c9697763e6f4d4fad9c5d9d2f11114a2.poster.avif?t=1763136040\" width=800 height=482 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/c9697763e6f4d4fad9c5d9d2f11114a2.webm?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/c9697763e6f4d4fad9c5d9d2f11114a2.mp4?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each successful run grants you a permanent reward that you can use during your journey. Even failed runs leave you with some resources that you can use in your Road House to grow stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your weapons and your chopper. Inject Abyssal Ink to make tattoos of power. And don't forget to buy drinks for the road from the mysterious bartender.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/0edc44b75396fec235aceff2c67be0d8.poster.avif?t=1763136040\" width=800 height=482 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/0edc44b75396fec235aceff2c67be0d8.webm?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/0edc44b75396fec235aceff2c67be0d8.mp4?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The purpose of killing procedurally generated demon bosses of Forsaken Lands is to eventually gain keys that allow you to descend into the Depths of Hell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Breaking subsequent seals of Hell introduces new enemies, encounters and events that you can find during your hunts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each domain of Hell features a unique demon lord that unlocks your further progress when slain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/ed0f520be0fbdfa717cc7163007ad9d0.poster.avif?t=1763136040\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/ed0f520be0fbdfa717cc7163007ad9d0.webm?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/ed0f520be0fbdfa717cc7163007ad9d0.mp4?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Abyss Chaser is an action game with heavy gameplay focus but it also has a deep lore and an engaging narrative side.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll uncover the story of Abaddon getting betrayed and join him on a path to clear his name and get back what he lost.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Abyss Chaser is an action rogue-like dungeon crawler that combines melee and ranged combat with supernatural themes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a path of vengeance as Abaddon - wrongfully disgraced rebel angel who travels the forsaken wasteland on his motorcycle hunting demons.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/3270ee2d6dbc6a5add622a2d75b90ee7.poster.avif?t=1763136040\" width=800 height=482 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/3270ee2d6dbc6a5add622a2d75b90ee7.webm?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/3270ee2d6dbc6a5add622a2d75b90ee7.mp4?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow in power during your Hunts, build your arsenal of weapons, gain support of otherworldly patrons and reclaim what's rightfully yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Abyss Chaser you complete Hunts in procedurally generated levels searching for one of demons that corrupt this land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For every run you can choose your equipment: Blade, Gun and a magical Amulet. You also get random spells and abilities from patrons that support you during the Hunt.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/c9697763e6f4d4fad9c5d9d2f11114a2.poster.avif?t=1763136040\" width=800 height=482 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/c9697763e6f4d4fad9c5d9d2f11114a2.webm?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/c9697763e6f4d4fad9c5d9d2f11114a2.mp4?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each successful run grants you a permanent reward that you can use during your journey. Even failed runs leave you with some resources that you can use in your Road House to grow stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your weapons and your chopper. Inject Abyssal Ink to make tattoos of power. And don't forget to buy drinks for the road from the mysterious bartender.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/0edc44b75396fec235aceff2c67be0d8.poster.avif?t=1763136040\" width=800 height=482 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/0edc44b75396fec235aceff2c67be0d8.webm?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/0edc44b75396fec235aceff2c67be0d8.mp4?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The purpose of killing procedurally generated demon bosses of Forsaken Lands is to eventually gain keys that allow you to descend into the Depths of Hell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Breaking subsequent seals of Hell introduces new enemies, encounters and events that you can find during your hunts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each domain of Hell features a unique demon lord that unlocks your further progress when slain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/ed0f520be0fbdfa717cc7163007ad9d0.poster.avif?t=1763136040\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/ed0f520be0fbdfa717cc7163007ad9d0.webm?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273740/extras/ed0f520be0fbdfa717cc7163007ad9d0.mp4?t=1763136040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Abyss Chaser is an action game with heavy gameplay focus but it also has a deep lore and an engaging narrative side.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll uncover the story of Abaddon getting betrayed and join him on a path to clear his name and get back what he lost.</p>",
